reviewText: The train that stops at Willoughby it's one of the best Twilight Zone episodes ever!  I love anything with airplanes or trains and this show really  has lots of imagination! I really enjoyed the ride!  I love the simpler times! This episode brings me back to the good old days!
Actually, I like it very much.  The episode of "A Stop at Willoughby" well sums up how "push, push, PUSH" our society has become today!!
